      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape! It drives smoothly and has been well-loved. If you're looking for something dependable that still looks great on the road, this is the one. I\u2019m happy to answer any questions or have you come by for a test drive! Let's get you behind the wheel of this beauty.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation Carrera features the highly evolved 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant, utilizing VarioCam Plus for a broader torque curve and 320hp. The longitudinal G96 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile gear selection, paired with a chassis that retains its factory-spec rigidity. It is equipped with an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently refreshed cooling system, including a high-flow water pump. The suspension geometry is dialed in with Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring the hydraulic steering rack delivers the unmasked feedback enthusiasts demand. While the paint displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization of the drivetrain and the integrity of the multi-link rear suspension remain excellent.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Ready for sale.",
