      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of well-maintained quality, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, with only minor, negligible imperfections that one would expect from a car that has been driven with care. Step inside to find a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the leather remains soft and the carpets are spotless. Every feature, from the premium sound system to the heated seats and navigation, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, this car stands strong; it has a comprehensive service history, with a recent multi-point inspection, fresh fluids, and tires with plenty of tread remaining. It handles beautifully on the highway and provides a quiet, composed ride in the city. This is an honest, reliable car that has been garaged and treated with respect, ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
